# Web3signer keystore for the multi-validator stack lives here.
# After running `regenerate.sh`, copy keys/validator-1/key into a
# `<address-of-validator-1>.yaml` file in this directory using the
# `file-raw` shape documented in besu/web3signer/README.md.
#
# Or use HashiCorp Vault / AWS KMS / Azure Key Vault for production.
